text: The Captain's Table is a 1959 British comedy movie directed by Jack Lee and stars John Gregson, Peggy Cummins, Donald Sinden, Maurice Denham, Joan Sims, Oliver Reed, Reginald Beckwith. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1959 comedy movies Category:British comedy movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Jack Lee
